2019/04/25 17:41:53
select user_id,nt.user_account,user_nick,work_id,work_content,work_filepath,score from (select user_id,user_data.user_account,user_nick from user_data inner join user on user_data.user_account=user.user_account where user_data.class='18软件工程') as nt left join (select user_account,work_id,work_content,work_filepath,score from submit_work where work_id=5) as nt2 on nt.user_account=nt2.user_account order by nt.user_id asc
---------------------------------------

---------------------------------------
